concepts.MATERNAL_TETANUS_TOXOID_(TT)_IMMUNIZATIO: Historical tetanus toxoid immunization status recorded over maternal history. Includes current and previous immunizations over 5 years or more.
concepts.NUMBER_OF_ABORTIONS/MISCARRIAGES_18_DESC: The number of abortions or miscarriages a mother has had. To be included in Gravida/Parity/Abortion calculations.
concepts.GRAVIDA_17_DESC: The number of times a woman has been pregnant
concepts.ESTIMATED_DATE_OF_CONFINEMENT_16_DESC: An estimation of the date in which a mother will give birth to her child.
concepts.CURRENT_MEDICATIONS_30_DESC: Drugs that are ordered at a given patient encounter. Typically used in a set with other medication information.
concepts.HISTORY_OF_FETAL_MOVEMENT_37_DESC: Recent history of fetal movement as reported by mother.
concepts.MORE_THAN_2_SMALL_CUPS_(50_ML)_OF_ESPRES: More than 2 small cups (50 ml) of espresso
concepts.NUMBER_OF_PRIOR_STILLBIRTHS_20_DESC: The number of prior deliveries with stillbirths. Still birth means the baby was dead at the time of birth.
concepts.NUMBER_OF_PREVIOUS_CESAREAN_SECTIONS_23_: How many times did she undergo cesarean section for delivering baby?
concepts.DIASTOLIC_BLOOD_PRESSURE_49_DESC: A patient's diastolic blood pressure measurement (taken with a manual cuff in either a sitting or standing position)
concepts.BODY_MASS_INDEX_41_DESC:
Body Mass Index (BMI) is a relationship between weight and height that is associated with body fat and health risk.

The equation is BMI = body weight in kilograms/height in meters squared.
concepts.MORE_THAN_3_CUPS_(300ML)_OF_INSTANT_COFF: More than 3 cups (300ml) of instant coffee
concepts.WEEKS_OF_CURRENT_GESTATION_14_DESC: Current gestation in number of weeks
concepts.PAST_PREGNANCY_COMPLICATIONS_24_DESC: Complications seen during the previous pregnancies for women
concepts.FACE_OR_BROW_PRESENTATION_OF_FOETUS_52: Face or brow presentation of foetus
concepts.SYSTOLIC_BLOOD_PRESSURE_48_DESC: A patient's systolic blood pressure measurement (taken with a manual cuff in either a sitting or standing position)
concepts.TOTAL_WEIGHT_GAIN_DURING_CURRENT_PREGNAN: Total weight gain during current pregnancy
concepts.NUMBER_OF_LIVE_DELIVERIES_19_DESC: Number of deliveries with live births. It is different from total number of deliveries or living children which are different concepts.
concepts.REASON_CLINICAL_ENQUIRY_FOR_INTIMATE_PAR: Reason clinical enquiry for intimate partner violence (IPV) was not done
concepts.METHOD_OF_GESTATIONAL_AGE_DETERMINATION_: How was the gestational age of fetus determined for pregnancy?
concepts.OBSTETRIC_ULTRASOUND_DONE_DURING_PREGNAN: Was an Ultrasound (Sonogram) done during pregnancy?
concepts.HIGHEST_EDUCATION_LEVEL_9_DESC: The highest level of formal education (Qualitative rather than quantitative. For Quantitative see Concept 1545.
concepts.BLOOD_GLUCOSE_TEST_TYPE_56_DESC: Type of blood glucose test performed.
concepts.MORE_THAN_2_CUPS_(200ML)_OF_FILTERED_OR_: More than 2 cups (200ml) of filtered or commercially brewed coffee
concepts.PARITY_21_DESC: The number of children a woman has delivered.
concepts.DATE_OF_LAST_MENSTRUAL_PERIOD_11_DESC: Date of last menstrual period for woman of childbearing age.
concepts.FETAL_PRESENTATION_52_DESC: the part of the fetus which lies closest to or has entered the true pelvis.
concepts.BODY_POSITION_50_DESC: Body position for procedure or blood pressure measurement
concepts.CLINICAL_ENQUIRY_FOR_INTIMATE_PARTNER_VI: Clinical enquiry for intimate partner violence (IPV)
concepts.DANGER_SIGNS,_PREGNANCY_4_DESC: The signs and symptoms during the pregnancy which might suggest danger to mother or baby Some of them are: vaginal bleeding, abdominal/pelvic pain, gush of fluid from vagina, swelling of hands and face, headache and blurring of vision, no fetal movements and others.
